name: Cait Sidhe
description:
Made in two weeks for the GameMaker Studio 2 Beta Jam 2. Third place winner following Magic Astronauts and Glitch Witches! Check out the results here!


Cait Sidhe is a fairy creature, a large black cat said to steal souls and transform. You are sent out into the woods to find and retrieve three magical items for your master, but must make it back before your nine lives are up.
